<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA523_03_IH_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema523_03.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_03_ih_0004">
      <section class="title type2" lang="y">
        <h2 data-head="4" class="is_star" lang="y">두 사각형은 서로 합동입니다. 각 ㄴㄷㄹ의 크기는 몇 도인지 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box align_center justify_center">
          <div class="img_area">
            <img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA523_03_IH/0004_01.png" alt="" />
            <span class="text text1">55º</span>
            <span class="text text2">115º</span>
            <span class="text text3">85º</span>
          </div>
          <div class="input_area flex align_center gap_10 ml_60">
            <span>(</span>
            <div class="input_wrap hint_up">
              <math-field data-answer-single="105 " text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span>º)</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">
                  각 ㄷㄹㄱ의 대응각은 각 ㅁㅂㅅ이고 대응각의 크기가 서로 같으므로 <br />
                  (각 ㄷㄹㄱ)=(각 ㅁㅂㅅ) =85°입니다.
                </p>
                <p lang="y">➔ (각 ㄴㄷㄹ)=360°-55°-115°-85°=105°</p>
                <p class="text_label">
                  <span class="label reference">참고</span>
                  <span lang="y">사각형의 네 각의 크기의 합은 360°입니다. </span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key" lang="y">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
